
TY  - JOUR
T1  - Choices and Outcomes in Assignment Mechanisms: The Allocation of Deceased Donor Kidneys
AU  - Agarwal, Nikhil
AU  - Hodgson, Charles
AU  - Somaini, Paulo
Y1  - 2025/03/01
PY  - 2025
DA  - 2025/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA20203
T2  - Econometrica
